<div id="c1">
<p>Now, that&#8217;s a timely rant.</p>

<p>Everybody and their brother seem to be freeing data nowadays, but - for some odd reason - the actual uses (and perhaps even professional evaluation) are then put too far aside.</p>

<p>How does your rant add up to what Watchdog is up to currently? Are you looking for journalists, or&#8230;</p>

